body:
### EnumerableExtensions [[page](http://tchatzigiannakis.github.io/enumerableextensions/)] [[repo](https://github.com/TChatzigiannakis/enumerableextensions)]
A collection of useful extension methods for IEnumerable<T>, mostly following the spirit of existing LINQ extension methods.

### EnvyLauncher [[repo](https://github.com/TChatzigiannakis/EnvyLauncher)]
A very simple application launcher for Windows that allows visual modification of environment variables passed to the child process.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
